com.tlswe.awsmock.cloudwatch.control

Class MockCloudWatchQueryHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tlswe.awsmock.cloudwatch.control.MockCloudWatchQueryHandler

  • public final class MockCloudWatchQueryHandler
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that handlers requests of AWS CloudWatch Query API for monitoring the mock ec2 instances. This class works between All object of mock CloudWatch.
